{
  "stem": "4032.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were forming a Polish army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, they didn't want to take the Jews to the army, but that's another thing, another [INAUDIBLE], I mean, in the history of--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So even the same thing, a friend of mine told me that after the war, he came to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was after the war, and he survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he thought, now, it's going to be better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Pollocks went and made a pogrom against Jews, and they killed about 13 people at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was a big struggle to survive as a Jew with the whole war because everybody was infected with Nazism and-- and their ideas.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were-- so you were-- but you were traveling with-- with the Polish?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of Poles, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of Poles traveled with us, the ones that were arrested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, there were more, I think, more Jews than Poles because Jews were running away from Germany, even Russian Jews from all Ukraine that the Germans-- that's why they attacked.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because Ukraine borders with Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Poland-- that's where they came from, the German army, and attacked the Russians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Tashkent?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably three weeks, also about three weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we got there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At least it was warm there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, Siberia is cold and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] desert-like.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's not desert, but it's no-- no inhabitants.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And over there, there was a lot of people because it was very fertile, the-- the whole area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had a lot of oil there, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where they were concentrating more on this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's where we went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because it was warmer there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You could sleep outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You could sleep inside and not freeze to death.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
